[I] A sound editor

[T] Snd is a sound editor modelled loosely after Emacs. It can accommodate any
[T] number of sounds, each with any number of channels. It can be customized
[T] and extended using Guile, Ruby, or Forth.

[U] https://snd.sourceforge.net

